{
  "texts": [
    "The latter criteria ranged from university professors and scientists to bankers and entrepreneurs with in-depth knowledge of DeFi.",
    "The experts were invited to answer the survey by e-mail or online messaging service to provide them with the highest possible convenience.Possible panelists were identified through four sources: first, panel candidates were identified as managers working for companies that are active in the DeFi space.",
    "Second, they were identified as attendees of conferences relating to the topic of DeFi.",
    "Third, participants were found using the business network LinkedIn, and, fourth, they were discovered using snowball sampling, i.e.",
    "by referrals of experts who were already participating."
  ]
}